An '''unidentified submerged object''' ('''USO''') is an unidentified object submerged in [[water]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/10/21/mysterious-craft-off-coast-of-sweden-sparks-hunt-for-uso-unidentified-submerged-object-4914260/|title=Mysterious craft off coast of Sweden sparks hunt for USO (Unidentified Submerged Object)|date=21 October 2014|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/567017/20140922/ufo-uso-aliens-space-unidentified-flying-object.htm |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-12-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228180914/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/567017/20140922/ufo-uso-aliens-space-unidentified-flying-object.htm |archivedate=2014-12-28 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/05/31/baltic-sea-ufo-hunters_n_1556150.html|title=Baltic Sea UFO Hunters Look To Identify Mystery Object|first=Lee|last=Speigel|date=31 May 2012|publisher=|via=Huff Post}}</ref> The term does not necessarily refer to an object of [[paranormal]] origin.
